EventArgsManagerNotify Members

EventArgsManagerNotify Class  Constructors  Methods  Properties  See Also

A general event args object for getting information about an notification. Has three general string arguments which have different meanings for different notifications. When NotifyCode is PULSER_RCVR_DISCOVERED, args are model, serial Num, and Pulser Index Number when NotifyCode is CURRENT_PULSER_RCVR_CHANGED, args are model, serial Num, and Pulser Index Number when NotifyCode is PULSER_RCVR_DETACH, args are model, ser#, prindex, bWasSelected is true if currently selected when NotifyCode is PROPERTY_CHANGE, args are model, ser#, prindex, and the property name when NotifyCode is ERROR, args are exception type, message, inner exception type if exists.
